channel.title: The Flow of How Anything Here Gets Done
channel.description: Propose Topic on Suggestions --> Watch as Idiots argue about it --> Finally agree it should be implemented --> Mods discuss it in a private and hidden manner --> ??? --> Wait for MITB to login so we can propose it --> MITB sends one word per day per week in response to the idea --> Wait for message to be received --> Realize message is encrypted and we need cipher key --> Wait half a year for MITB to send cipher key --> Forget/Abandon idea --> Return to start :D
